		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Twin Claws",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The Mula is in frenzy thanks to Voracious Rage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The Mula attempts two claw Strikes against a creature within reach, each using the mula's current multiple attack penalty. If both attacks hit, the mula combines their damage and then add any other applicable effects from both attacks. The mula adds any precision damage only once, to the attack of her choice. Combine the damage from both Strikes and apply resistances and weaknesses only once. This counts as two attacks when calculating the mula's multiple attack penalty.</p><p></p>",
